VERSION 1.1.0
------------------------
   o Added T_regularization = "low_rank" (T = U * t(V))
     to structurally bound T capacity and prevent H_Sym collapse
   o Fixed frobenius_unit list-mode crash: use single global RMS
     scalar instead of per-chrom scalars, with eps guard
   o Documented dimnames assignment algorithm in @details
     (background-absorbing "comp_*" components)

VERSION 1.0.0
------------------------
   o Added Machima2() for symmetric epigenomic matrices
     (X_Epi ~ G * H_Sym * t(G), where G = T * W_RNA)
   o Added init_W_RNA/init_H_RNA/init_H_Sym, fixH_Sym to Machima2()
   o Added T_regularization ("frobenius_unit", "l2") to Machima2()
   o Added nmf_init_n_restart/num_iter/algorithm params
   o Exported Mat2List()
   o Fixed NA in dimnames when J > num_celltypes
   o Fixed BetaDivergence formula (operator precedence + X/Y swap)
   o Fixed L1_W_RNA unused in W_RNA updates
   o Fixed horizontal mode RecError mismatch

VERSION 0.99.0
------------------------
   o Package released
